# Copy this to .env.local for local dev, or set in your deploy host's env vars.
# NOTHING here is required — every feature has a free / no-config default.

# ---- Database (libSQL / Turso) ----
# Local dev: defaults to file:./local.db if omitted (zero setup).
# Production (Vercel): create a free Turso DB at https://turso.tech and set both.
# DATABASE_URL=libsql://your-db-name.turso.io
# DATABASE_AUTH_TOKEN=eyJh...your-token...

# ---- AI copy generation ----
# We do NOT need a server-side key — AI copy is bring-your-own-key. Users paste
# their Anthropic key in the browser; it's stored in localStorage and proxied
# through /api/ai/generate without being logged.
#
# Only set ANTHROPIC_MODEL if you want to swap from the default sonnet 4.6.
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6

# ---- Site URL (for OG image absolute URLs) ----
# Vercel sets VERCEL_URL automatically. Override here if you have a custom domain.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://waitlistkit.com

# ---- Stripe billing ----
# Optional. Without these, /api/billing/checkout runs in dev mode and just
# flips the cookie owner's plan locally. Useful for demos. To take real
# money, set all four and `npm i stripe`.
#
# Create products + prices in Stripe dashboard, then paste price IDs here.
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_...
# STRIPE_PRICE_PRO=price_...
# STRIPE_PRICE_TEAM=price_...
# STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...    (from `stripe listen` or webhook dashboard)
